{"tid":2050943,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"屋宇署：總狗司黃維的寓所天台屋屬僭建 業主承諾清拆","createTime":"2020-06-04T12:01:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T12:18:04.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"26472e2c5f046a94ed41a99ce4d78fdd03f08fd1","tid":2050943,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T12:01:47.000Z","msg":"屋宇署：O記總警司黃維的寓所天台屋屬僭建<br />\n04.06.2020 19:48<br />\n<br />\n屋宇署派員到有組織罪案及三合會調查科總警司黃維，位於大埔錦麗園的寓所視察，發現天台有僭建物，屋宇署說，僭建物沒有明顯危險，業主已通知屋宇署，短期內會拆除相，因此會暫緩執法行動，但會跟進清拆進度。<br />\n<br />\n助理警務處長陶輝早前亦被揭發所居住的村屋有僭建物，以及霸佔官地，地政總署已向陶輝發警告信，要求糾正違規僭建，並停止佔用政府用地。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1299531&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1299531%26csid%3D261_341&d=Fi4Me5dMHeyo7M%2BwlVraY0pSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=d7a71621\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1299531&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【知法犯法】O記總警司黃維疑僭建300呎玻璃屋 地政今巡視<br />\n更新時間 (HKT): 2020.05.19 22:00<br />\n<br />\n<code>節錄</code><br />\n有組織罪案及三合會調查科總警司黃維居住的大埔錦麗園單位，昨（18日）被揭發天台疑有僭建物。今午有地政處人員到場巡視，並一度到黃維單位外視察，職員回應記者則稱是「例行巡視」，未有回應是否針對黃維單位。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200519/BWPDLCFSXI2BIOJFFMDKUSDTSE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200519%2FBWPDLCFSXI2BIOJFFMDKUSDTSE%2F&d=Fi4Me5dMHeyo7M%2BwlVraY0pSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=0ffc1e4b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200519%2FBWPDLCFSXI2BIOJFFMDKUSDTSE%2F&h=e8ca3277\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200519/BWPDLCFSXI2BIOJFFMDKUSDTSE/</a>"},{"pid":"f31f884de946be3e253ad52eafb5dacde9cbfc27","tid":2050943,"uid":132587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T12:08:17.000Z","msg":"原來做錯左改番就可以當乜事都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fd575ae1956f392dfd31c061985e185211ef9f3","tid":2050943,"uid":308251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f31f884de946be3e253ad52eafb5dacde9cbfc27","tid":2050943,"uid":132587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T12:08:17.000Z","msg":"原來做錯左改番就可以當乜事都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T12:18:04.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係, 所以法律面前, 窮人含撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}